      "role": "user",
      "content": "just sitting here in paris looking at the lights and honestly... it feels like i've seen enough. i've done the tours, checked the boxes, seen the sights. i feel like i'm at the end of my itinerary and there just isn't anything left to see. i'm just so tired of the trip.",
